      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready for a new home, this is the one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
