    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather is supple and free of any creases or wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at the dealership with a complete, documented maintenance history included. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. If you are looking for a turn-key, investment-grade experience with no compromises, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
